title: Ep. - 249 - BRANDON MILLS FROM THE BACHELOR: LISTEN TO YOUR HEART DIRECTOR OF AUTISM: THE SEQUEL
description:
Brandon Mills from The Bachelor: Listen To Your Heart explains how he was cast for the show, what it was like to live with other musicians, and serenades Kate with his original song.

 

Tricia Regan, Director of HBO’s 'Autism: The Sequel' talks about the film, which tells the story of five children who have been impacted with autism in very different ways, and are now adolescents with a burgeoning sense of independence and desire to make it on their own.
